transcripts.transcript: Thank you for your patience. Your waiting time is longer than expected. Would you like to receive a call back when someone's available? Enter a pound sign to accept the callback on your current number, or 1 to dial a new one we can use to reach out to you. Your position on the queue will not be lost. You are currently caller number 2 waiting to speak with a representative. Thank you for your patience.
